WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:08.518
Hello, Miss Billy. This is Brandon. Of course you know, but I just had this visitation that I have to tell you about privately on this.

00:00:08.519 --> 00:00:11.915
I'm sitting here after it was over, and the Lord said, "Make a video.

00:00:11.916 --> 00:00:18.286
Don't call her on the phone, just tell her."So, this is what I saw: I saw Lucy.

00:00:18.287 --> 00:00:27.050
I saw Brother Halverson. I saw Jeannie Wilkerson. And they were... I'll tell you what I saw.

00:00:27.051 --> 00:00:36.196
I was interceding and all of a sudden tonight, I was caught up in the spirit, and I got taken, and I was hearing people sing with me.

00:00:36.197 --> 00:00:49.913
And I was singing, "From glory to glory, He's changing me, changing me."And all of a sudden, I heard other voices in my room singing this song with me as I was worshiping in the glory.

00:00:49.914 --> 00:00:52.789
And Diana could smell the fragrance of the Father and Jesus.

00:00:52.790 --> 00:01:04.263
"I'm here with you."And all of a sudden, I could hear, "From glory to glory, He's changing us."And it was beautiful singing, and I was like...

00:01:04.264 --> 00:01:21.063
I noticed that voice before. That's Lucy, Lynn's sister. I said, "Honey, I hear her voice."And all of a sudden, I was taken up, and I went through like this pillar, this shaft of a tunnel.

00:01:21.064 --> 00:01:26.639
It was like a tunnel, and all of a sudden, I went through this tunnel, and there was purple, and there were clouds, and it was beautiful.

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:34.215
And I went up through it, and I could see into heaven. And I said, "Lord, what is this?"He said, "This is the great cloud of witnesses, Brandon.

00:01:34.216 --> 00:01:51.599
They're praying with you tonight."And I could hear Sister Lucy interceding for America and...

00:01:51.600 --> 00:02:02.083
I'll try to do this without crying. I could hear her singing, praying for her sister, Lynn. And I could hear her interceding for Minnesota.

00:02:02.084 --> 00:02:07.263
And she was saying, "Minnesota, Minnesota,"and she was praying in tongues, a heavenly tongue.

00:02:07.264 --> 00:02:14.770
It was glorious. And they were interceding in heaven for America, for a revival.

00:02:14.771 --> 00:02:18.769
And I could see Brother Halverson, and they were praying together.

00:02:18.770 --> 00:02:24.465
And I could see Jeannie Wilkerson and Rachel Tippet Teafatiller, and there were two other people.

00:02:24.466 --> 00:02:31.585
I don't know who they were, but they were sitting on a patchwork quilt.

00:02:31.586 --> 00:02:42.933
I can describe it to you: Lucy was sitting in a rocking chair that was like a beautiful, old, oak rocking chair.

00:02:42.934 --> 00:02:49.722
It was all Southern-looking. It was beautiful. And they were sitting on a grassy meadow with a beautiful oak tree.

00:02:49.723 --> 00:02:53.602
And this oak tree was gorgeous, and there was no darkness in it at all.

00:02:53.603 --> 00:03:03.999
None of the leaves had shadows. All of this oak tree was beautiful, shining bright. And I could see it as I was looking through this portal.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:11.697
And I could see Jeannie Wilkerson was sitting next to this lady that had a bun in her hair.

00:03:11.698 --> 00:03:22.318
She looked like she had a big, Holy Ghost Pentecostal haircut, like her hair was pulled up and it was in a bun on top of a bun.

00:03:22.319 --> 00:03:28.058
She looked like an old Pentecostal woman, and they were all travailing for Minnesota.

00:03:28.059 --> 00:03:35.425
And I could see Brother Halverson, but they looked young-looking.

00:03:35.426 --> 00:03:41.911
Of course, they were in their glorified bodies, but the Lord said, "Brandon, they're interceding for the revival.

00:03:41.912 --> 00:03:46.269
They're travailing for the revival."But as I could see... Okay.

00:03:46.270 --> 00:03:53.450
Oh, the Lord said, "Don't skip around."I got to tell you about the patchwork quilt. The patchwork quilt had pastel colors.

00:03:53.451 --> 00:04:05.056
I could see purple, blue, pink, and white on this quilt that Sister Wilkerson was sitting on with these other women.

00:04:05.057 --> 00:04:10.073
And like I said, Lucy was in the chair. And Brother Halverson was sitting next to Lucy.

00:04:10.075 --> 00:04:24.009
And I could see him, and I could see the quilt was on the ground, but there were flowers, these beautiful little daisies on top of the purple square-looking quilt pattern.

00:04:24.010 --> 00:04:37.448
And each daisy was perfectly in a row. And I could see yellow threads come up through where each square would be connected to each other.

00:04:37.449 --> 00:04:43.679
In those little squares were little yellow threads that were like bows.

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:52.075
Beautiful little bows were inside of those little squares of this patchwork quilt, and they were having intercession.

00:04:52.076 --> 00:05:04.945
And all of a sudden, I could see Minnesota, and then Lynn Hammond's church became on fire, and a great wave of the glory of God...

00:05:04.946 --> 00:05:18.991
The Lord said to me, He said, "I visited it once before. But what I'm about to do at Living Word, son, will dwarf what I've done before.

00:05:18.992 --> 00:05:26.662
For a great, mighty harvest, a great move of My presence will visit in another generation.

00:05:26.663 --> 00:05:31.838
For I visited this generation, Lynn, and a new way for a new generation.

00:05:31.839 --> 00:05:37.037
A new way for a new generation is what the Father said. A new way for a new generation.

00:05:37.038 --> 00:05:51.275
And I will visit Living Word one more time with this great move of My presence."And I saw a glorious fire all over Living Word Church there in Minnesota.

00:05:51.276 --> 00:06:13.839
And I heard Brother Halverson was praying, "Minnesota, Minnesota."And he was travailing, "Minnesota."And he was calling for revival, "Minnesota, Minnesota."And he was travailing over this as I was hearing it echo as Lucy was rocking in this chair, and they were both praying back and forth with each other, and I heard it.

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:34.500
But this was what was amazing: as it was being travailed in heaven, their prayers went through that portal and it hit me in the chest, and it caused the prayer to come through me, and I started groaning the prayer out in the spirit realm that was happening in heaven.

00:06:34.501 --> 00:06:40.732
It came through the portal and hit my stomach, and it started to travail through me.

00:06:40.733 --> 00:06:44.363
And the Lord said, "Pray it out. They're helping you. Pray it out.

00:06:44.364 --> 00:06:47.314
They're helping you. There's a great revival coming to Branson.

00:06:47.315 --> 00:06:52.395
There's a great revival coming to Collinsville. You must help them.

00:06:52.396 --> 00:07:21.439
Pray, pray, pray."And yes, He said heaven. I'm trying to get all...

00:07:21.440 --> 00:07:23.594
I could feel the glory when I started talking about it again.

00:07:23.595 --> 00:07:44.052
I could see it, baby. Okay. Heaven and earth are going to collide. The Lord said heaven and earth are going to collide.

00:07:44.053 --> 00:07:58.249
And He said, "In one moment, in everything that I've ever desired, the greatest harvest of souls, Brandon, everything's going to change in a 24-hour period. Watch September. Watch these months ahead.

00:07:58.250 --> 00:08:11.753
For the birthing pains and the labor pains will increase upon the earth, but My glorious church, Brandon, will rise with a great fire, without spot, without wrinkle, what we've all been believing for.

00:08:11.754 --> 00:08:17.972
But it will be the greatest outpouring of the Spirit of the Lord."And I saw Minnesota, and I've never seen Minnesota.

00:08:17.973 --> 00:08:21.300
But the Lord said, "Brandon, Minnesota, Minnesota, Minnesota.

00:08:21.301 --> 00:08:25.279
Watch what I do in Minnesota."And I saw a revival coming to Minnesota.

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:29.429
And I saw a revival coming to Branson. I saw a revival coming to Eagle Mountain Church.

00:08:29.430 --> 00:08:40.538
I saw a revival coming to Collinsville, Oklahoma."And He said, "Brandon, there's going to be hot spots throughout the world, around America."But He said, "Watch what I'm about to do.

00:08:40.539 --> 00:08:49.677
There'll be hot spots."And I was taken to ORU, and I saw the Mabee Center, and it was completely engulfed with the glory of God, and it was a flame of fire.

00:08:49.678 --> 00:08:59.049
It looked like a teardrop. It was fire, and the fire of God. And He said, "Brandon."And then He said, "I'm going to shake all the temples in India.

00:08:59.050 --> 00:09:08.231
I will shake the temples down, the false gods, and I'm going to break them down, and there's going to be major earthquakes."And I saw a major revival, a flood.

00:09:08.232 --> 00:09:12.172
He said, "I'm shaking it, Brandon, and I'm going to visit India.

00:09:12.173 --> 00:09:17.914
I'm going to visit China."And I saw a great revival coming in like we've never seen before in these areas.

00:09:17.915 --> 00:09:28.777
And so, it all came out of the prayer as Lucy and they were interceding for a revival for America, for heaven and earth are going to be invaded together.

00:09:28.778 --> 00:09:34.800
They're coming as one. And I said, "Oh, Jesus, what a time to be living in.

00:09:34.801 --> 00:09:37.994
What a time to be living in these last days, ladies and gentlemen.

00:09:37.995 --> 00:09:44.941
Oh, I'm not talking to my crowd. What a time to be living in. Jesus is coming.

00:09:44.942 --> 00:09:49.599
And so that's what I had for you. But it was so beautiful the way the cloud looked.

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:54.718
I wanted to see it. You've got to tell Miss Lynn, too. That would probably bless her.

00:09:54.719 --> 00:10:02.102
Maybe you tell Lynn. I just wanted to tell you, Miss Billy, because you're my friend.

00:10:02.103 --> 00:10:07.336
But I thought this is something that's so precious that I couldn't keep it to myself.

00:10:07.337 --> 00:10:23.952
I had to tell people what they're praying for us over there, our loved ones that have went home before us. And I don't even know Lucy. I don't even know these people.

00:10:23.953 --> 00:10:33.683
But they're praying for us, and they're interceding for Minnesota, and they're interceding for us—the great cloud of witnesses.

00:10:33.684 --> 00:10:43.364
Jesus is coming. And it's something that I'll never forget the rest of my life what Jesus just showed me.

00:10:43.365 --> 00:10:48.124
And it's so beautiful. Our Jeannie Wilkerson looks so nice.

00:10:48.125 --> 00:10:54.155
Her skin looked so young, and in every vision I saw, her skin was so young.

00:10:54.156 --> 00:11:00.716
And in all the things I've seen her, she looks so old, but she was so young and so fresh.

00:11:00.717 --> 00:11:09.065
I knew exactly who she was, and Rachel Tiller and this great cloud before us.

00:11:09.066 --> 00:11:17.440
God bless you. I just wanted to tell you about it. Thank you. Bye-bye."

